That's wonderful news, Noah. I'm feeling really relieved to have this sorted out.

I'm glad I could assist you, Carol. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that's all. Thank you so much, Noah.

You're welcome, Carol. Thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers and have a great day!
